headline: Evercore sees upside for Target, Best Buy on holiday shopping trends
summary: Investing.com -- Evercore ISI initiated positive tactical calls on Target Corporation (NYSE:TGT) and Best Buy Co Inc (NYSE:BBY) on improved holiday shopping trends and favourable spending intentions in key categories.
